            <title>[AVRO-835] C# code gen fails on for protocols</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-835</link>
                <project id="12310911" key="AVRO">Apache Avro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When code generating a protocol, such as AvroTrace, the C# code gen fails with a duplicate schema exception.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Avro.AvroException occurred&lt;br/&gt;
  Message=Duplicate schema name org.apache.avro.ipc.trace.&lt;br/&gt;
  Source=Avro&lt;br/&gt;
  StackTrace:&lt;br/&gt;
       at Avro.NamedSchema..ctor(Type type, SchemaName name, IList`1 aliases, PropertyMap props, SchemaNames names)&lt;br/&gt;
  InnerException: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will attach a unit test that shows the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
