                <project id="12310911" key="AVRO">Apache Avro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Following email conversation, this is a port of &lt;a href=&quot;https://bitbucket.org/tebeka/avrocat/src&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;avrocat&lt;/a&gt; to the avro code base.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
